import React from "react"
import { Button, Card, Stack, TextContainer,} from "@shopify/polaris"
const EmailPreview = () => {
    return (
        <Card title="Advanced Email Template Preview">
            <Card.Section>
                <Stack>
                    <Stack.Item fill><TextContainer>Get this template now by upgrading your plan</TextContainer></Stack.Item>
                    <Stack.Item><Button>Upgrade now</Button></Stack.Item>
                </Stack>
            </Card.Section>
        </Card>

    )
}

export default EmailPreview
